      "body" : "This is very odd.\r\nThe password is encoded as base64 before sending it in a HTTP header.\r\nIt should *never* end up in an URL. Where are you seeing this? Can you provide a traceback?\r\n\r\n(to be clear, I think changing it to use base58 makes sense, but I get slightly worried if passwords end up in URLs)",
